      "rationale": "SST k-ω turbulence model selected based on rotating machinery literature. Sensitivity study comparing k-ε realizable and RSM performed at two operating points; HI differences of 9–14% observed. Hemolysis power-law exponent sensitivity evaluated via ±10% perturbation. Model form uncertainty estimated at 12% of HI. Achieved level 3 falls one gradation below required level 4; gap accepted given Monte Carlo UQ coverage of parametric uncertainty.",
